## How to Run

**Backend:**
```bash
cd e:/hackathon/server
node server.js
# Running on http://localhost:3001
# WhatsApp QR code appears in terminal
```

**Frontend:**
```bash
cd e:/hackathon/client
npm run dev
# Running on http://localhost:5173
```

**WhatsApp Bot:**
1. Wait for QR code in backend terminal
2. Open WhatsApp → Linked Devices → Link a Device
3. Scan the QR code
4. Bot is now live — every incoming message is automatically categorized

**Bot Commands (send in any WhatsApp group):**
- `struct summary` → Bot replies with group summary
- `struct notes` → Bot replies with recent notes

---

## Categorization Rules

| Category | Keywords |
|---|---|
| Notes | assignment, notes, pdf, lecture, material, slides… |
| Announcements | deadline, schedule, exam date, class cancelled, reminder… |
| Doubts | ?, how, why, doubt, explain, can someone… |
| Important | urgent, important, must read, critical, asap… |
| General | (everything else) |

## Auto-Tags

`#Assignment` `#Exam` `#Project` `#Reminder` `#Notes` `#Important`
